  "html": "<!-- TODO (EJ): add your voice — factual stub. (You confirmed this can be shared.) Draft. -->\n<p class=\"\">A browser-based newspaper layout tool — a WordPress plugin, Nuxt web editor, and Slack bot — built to replace InDesign for small newsrooms. The editor offers a drag-drop frame-based layout system on a six-column grid with WordPress article import and AI-powered headline suggestions.</p>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Newswell Studio — drag-drop frame layout on the six-column grid\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/newswell/layout-1.png\" alt=\"Newswell Studio — drag-drop frame layout on the six-column grid\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/projects/newswell/layout-1.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/projects/newswell/layout-1.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/newswell/layout-1.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/projects/newswell/layout-1.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"Newswell Studio — drag-drop frame layout on the six-column grid\" width=\"3600\" height=\"2262\" style=\"--splay-rot:0.6deg;\" data-dimensions=\"3600×2262\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\">\n<figcaption class=\"\">Newswell Studio — drag-drop frame layout on the six-column grid</figcaption>\n</figure>\n<figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"Article trimming and page export\" class=\"\">\n<img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/projects/newswell/layout-2.png\" alt=\"Article trimming and page export\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_